trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo"></xref> objects.
The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo> class allows you to programmatically access and modify tag-prefix information stored in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo>类允许你以编程方式访问和修改标记前缀信息存储在配置文件。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo>

trans-unit.source: Tag prefixes associate a "namespace" in ASP.NET with the assemblies and namespaces that must be included for custom controls and user controls to work properly.
trans-unit.target: 标记前缀将在 ASP.NET 中的"命名空间"的程序集和命名空间必须包含自定义控件和用户控件，使其正常工作的相关联。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo> objects are stored as members of a TagPrefixCollection object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo>对象存储为 TagPrefixCollection 对象的成员。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo>

trans-unit.source: The TagPrefixCollection class allows you to programmatically access and modify the `controls` subsection of the `pages` section of a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: TagPrefixCollection 类允许你以编程方式访问和修改`controls`的小节`pages`配置文件节。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection"></xref> class.
The TagPrefixCollection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: TagPrefixCollection 构造函数不应在代码中直接使用。

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
trans-unit.target: 它是由 ASP.NET 配置系统调用的。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.Controls%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection> class always contains an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection> type.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.Controls%2A>属性<xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection>类始终包含的实例<xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection>类型。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.Controls%2A>
